(PH) {icon:bullet,1.2} While moving you gain {c_number}[{SF_2}*100|+%|]{/c} Dodge Chance or after standing still for {c_number}[{SF_7}]{/c} seconds you become {c_important}{u}Unstoppable{/u}{/c}.

{icon:bullet,1.2} When you Dodge or Block an attack you trigger a {c_number}[{SF_3}*100|%|]{/c} Thorns attack against the attacker.
